OL,3,C'Horrendous incident': Children
OL,4,Cplaying on footpath end up trapped
OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FThree children who were playing on a
OL,8,Ffootpath ended up trapped beneath a
OL,9,Fcar during a "horrendous incident" in
OL,10,FBelfast, a court has heard.
OL,12,FBelfast Magistrates' Court also heard
OL,13,Fthat a man accused of a number of
OL,14,Fmotoring offences left the scene
OL,15,Fwithout checking on the children,
OL,16,Fclimbed a fence and was discovered by
OL,17,Fpolice in a taxi.
