OL,3,C'Horrendous incident': Children
OL,4,Cplaying on footpath end up trapped
OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FThomas Noel Maughan, 37, from Black
OL,8,FRidge Gardens in Belfast, appeared in
OL,9,Fthe dock charged with driving with
OL,10,Fexcess alcohol, causing grievous
OL,11,Fbodily injury by dangerous driving and
OL,12,Ffailing to stop, failing to remain and
OL,13,Ffailing to report where an accident
OL,14,Foccurred causing injury.
OL,16,FA PSNI constable told the court on
OL,17,FTuesday she could connect Maughan to
OL,18,Fthe offences.
