OL,3,C'Horrendous incident': Children
OL,4,Cplaying on footpath end up trapped
OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FFollowing a defence application for
OL,8,Fbail, she told the court that shortly
OL,9,Fafter 5pm on Sunday police had
OL,10,Fresponded to a report of a collision
OL,11,Fin the Black Ridge View area of
OL,12,FBelfast where a woman told them her
OL,13,Ftwo children and their friend were
OL,14,Fplaying on the footpath when a car had
OL,15,Freversed over them and the driver had
OL,16,Fmade off and returned to another
OL,17,Faddress.
OL,19,FThe officer told the court that police
OL,20,Fhad visited the address but the driver
OL,21,Fwas not present.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
