OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FShe said the three children were taken
OL,8,Fto hospital suffering "potentially
OL,9,Fserious injuries".
OL,11,FThe constable told the court that
OL,12,Fpolice at the scene were notified by a
OL,13,Fmember of the public that the
OL,14,Fsuspected driver was in a taxi at the
OL,15,Fend of the street which was blocked by
OL,16,Femergency service vehicles.
OL,18,FHe was arrested at the scene.
