OL,3,C'Horrendous incident': Children
OL,4,Cplaying on footpath end up trapped
OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FThe officer said: "There was clear
OL,8,FCCTV of the incident which shows the
OL,9,Fdefendant getting into the car,
OL,10,Fdriving directly over the three
OL,11,Fchildren who are sat on the footpath.
OL,13,F"They are then trapped under his
OL,14,Fvehicle. The defendant reverses back
OL,15,Fover them, parking up his vehicle and
OL,16,Freturning to his address without
OL,17,Fchecking on the welfare of the
OL,18,Fchildren.
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@AOU
