OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,F"It then shows him jumping the back
OL,8,Ffence of the property immediately
OL,9,Fafter the incident."
OL,11,FThe officer said Maughan had made full
OL,12,Fadmissions during police interview to
OL,13,Fbeing the driver and to driving with
OL,14,Fexcess alcohol.
OL,16,FShe said: "Obviously, it is a
OL,17,Fhorrendous incident."
OL,19,FThe officer said one of the victims
OL,20,Fhad suffered a fractured pelvis.
