OL,3,C'Horrendous incident': Children
OL,4,Cplaying on footpath end up trapped
OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FSetting out police objections to bail,
OL,8,Fshe said: "He was intoxicated through
OL,9,Falcohol, but also the fact he has made
OL,10,Foff from the scene without checking
OL,11,Fthe welfare (of the children), it
OL,12,Fcould have been a much worse incident
OL,13,Fconsidering what happened.
OL,15,F"He showed a complete disregard for
OL,16,Fpublic safety while driving while
OL,17,Fintoxicated."
OL,19,FShe said police believed releasing him
OL,20,Fon bail would result in a risk to the
OL,21,Fpublic and to Maughan's own safety.
