OL,3,C'Horrendous incident': Children
OL,4,Cplaying on footpath end up trapped
OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FA defence lawyer told the court that a
OL,8,Fyoung boy had been lying flat on the
OL,9,Ffootpath and two girls were drawing
OL,10,Faround him with chalk.
OL,12,FHe said his client had got into his
OL,13,Fcar and driven a small distance
OL,14,Fforward and could not see the children.
OL,16,FHe added: "He hears the screaming and
OL,17,Fimmediately reverses.
OL,19,F"It is very clear, if he hadn't
OL,20,Freversed the vehicle that young boy
OL,21,Fwould be dead today."
OL,26,@xD@KOU{D@AOU}D@UO]
