OL,3,C'Horrendous incident': Children
OL,4,Cplaying on footpath end up trapped
OL,5,Cbeneath car
OL,7,FThe lawyer said that by reversing his
OL,8,Fcar, Maughan had allowed the boy to
OL,9,Fget up.
OL,11,FRegarding the CCTV footage, he said:
OL,12,F"It is awful footage, I have watched
OL,13,Fit. It is very difficult viewing."
OL,15,FThe lawyer said his client had left
OL,16,Fthe scene because be believed his
OL,17,Fpresence there was a distraction.
OL,19,FHe said the issue in the case would be
OL,20,Fthe standard of driving and whether it
OL,21,Famounted to careless or dangerous.
