OL,7,FThe solicitor said Maughan's family
OL,8,Fwere in court.
OL,10,FThe district judge said it was an
OL,11,F"appalling set of facts" and refused
OL,12,Fbail.
OL,14,FMaughan will appear in court again on
OL,15,FSeptember 23.
